    "en": {
      "title": "Tourist arrivals are increasing",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Sri Lanka Tourism Development Authority, 32865 tourists visited Sri Lanka in June which is slightly more than the previous months. Sri Lanka Tourism Development Authority said that 30207 tourists visited Sri Lanka in May.",
        "6550 tourists from India and 3199 tourists from Britain visited Sri Lanka, 2448 tourists came to Sri Lanka for Australia Sri Lanka cricket series."
      ],
